name: REACT!
description: "REACT!" is an animation loop that I made with my friends. It's a "tradigital" frame by frame piece made to look like an 80's cartoon. I was in charge of the script, the direction, and the designs of the character and the background. Animation by @bruks_but_in_2d and @breminho, post production by @pedro.h.s.magalhaes, sound FX by @afranio.magalhaes and sound track by @junk.ie (all @s are for instagram profiles).
